jhH7ldnBfw48FHJ___Q1gTn34HRz3YqzZkaut7TeMoQ&oe=66EEB26F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "PUB_HOLOTANKS_Landscape_2560x1440.png", "id": "1474100426494212", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86604447_1474100429827545_434446056725707431_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=fR1QeWqUlnQQ7kNvgFJnJXI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA8dLmKXRnzPsVEY-nogu4rorOPfxBprVyElSmok3c-Cg&oe=66EEA31D"}, "display_name": "Holotanks (BETA)", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Holotanks, a furious action game that revolutionizes the concept of the future of toys, is a truly room-scale co-located Mixed Reality toy tank battle game! \nWith both single-player and multiplayer modes, it transforms your room into a dynamic battlefield!\n\nFeatures:\n- Future of toys - tanks battle in your room!\n- True room-scale fun gameplay - adapts to any room size\n- 8 game modes to play alone or with friends\n- Remote and  co-located multiplayer - up to 8 players in the same room \n- Rich Single-Player campaign\n- Built-in level editor\n- Unlockable tank parts and skins\n\nTurn your own living room into a tank battle!\n(and please remember this is a Beta version)", "short_description": "Turn your own living room into a tank battle! Holotanks is a action packed truly room-scale co-located Mixed Reality toy tanks game featuring SP and MP modes. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://beatshapers.com/holotanks_privacy.txt", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Fortell Games Inc", "support_website_url": "https://www.fortell.games/", "website_url": "https://www.fortell.games/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_